{"id": 2133, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得有哪些“识相”“懂事”细思恐极？", "description": "那些扭曲的规训都是怎么一点一滴影响人的。", "record_count": 4679, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180122181912Dx2UnBNjhtKw9eE5.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-23T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 261120, "content": "指责提出问题的人为什么要提，并进行羞辱，认为提出问题是一种不懂事。反正把提出问题的人解决了，问题就不会被发现了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217462}, {"id": 261632, "content": "随大流准没错", "image": "img/option/option/201801250235467RsciwMISCrTOgvy", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073583}, {"id": 261121, "content": "我错了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240775}, {"id": 261122, "content": "差不多就可以了…按部就班中规中矩是懂事", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244954}, {"id": 261123, "content": "盲从", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184289}, {"id": 261126, "content": "网上所谓的键盘侠吧。其实好多人根本不知道事情的真实经过，他们看到键盘侠的各种怼怼怼，就下意识跟着怼了。还是希望每个人都有自己的思想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244970}, {"id": 261638, "content": "我很关心你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225922}, {"id": 261127, "content": "爱情经过反反复复的分分合合，最后‘修成正果’\n大多数人称之为，《我的恋爱观》——这就是幸福。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210956}, {"id": 261128, "content": "爱情经过反反复复分分合合，最终‘修成正果’\n大多数人得出的结论，《我的恋爱观》——这就是真爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210956}, {"id": 261129, "content": "大人说话小孩子不要多嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244977}, {"id": 261132, "content": "国企职场中的懂事:明明是领导犯的错，但是事发的时候，我就算挨顿骂或者被惩罚，也不敢说出半点事实，不敢据理力争", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244988}, {"id": 262669, "content": "我性格弱又很爱男友，时间长了对他一些事也就忍了算了，他说我最懂事。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 261133, "content": "为了博取父母“听话”的标签，忍让一切，即使自己不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241360}, {"id": 261134, "content": "你这么笨，不属于这行", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244995}, {"id": 261135, "content": "嗯好的\n我知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843691}, {"id": 261136, "content": "人人都认为你懂事 当你又哭又闹的时候就是不对的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995565}, {"id": 261139, "content": "很多人都曲解了懂事的含义，正如沉默的大多数\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233964}, {"id": 261395, "content": "父母懂得比成年孩子多？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661570}, {"id": 261140, "content": "明明心情不好，为了不影响别人，假装自己很开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244998}, {"id": 261141, "content": "可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133650}, {"id": 261142, "content": "你忙吧，不打扰你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697938}, {"id": 266010, "content": "很不礼貌地问我很多我不想回答的东西，不回答就一遍一遍不停下\n父母夸她开朗，让我多学学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267242}, {"id": 261147, "content": "解释＝找理由", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245031}, {"id": 261403, "content": "父母说什么都听，因为父母反对连自己相爱多年的恋人都可以抛弃，还要打着孝顺的名义", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245595}, {"id": 261148, "content": "扭曲的培训就是强制性的让人凌晨三点半就起床然后行走几十公里的山路，还美其名曰培训团队的协作能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245034}, {"id": 261149, "content": "我们永远都是最好的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245035}, {"id": 261150, "content": "我们永远都是最好的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245035}, {"id": 261153, "content": "别讲真话", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 261154, "content": "你不喝就是不给我面子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245049}, {"id": 261155, "content": "现在学会了虚伪", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133920}, {"id": 260901, "content": "父母一吵架孩子就显得很乖，大人把孩子的恐惧和讨好称为懂事", "image": null, "praise_count": 768, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 261157, "content": "读书太多就会变得眼界高，高不成低不就。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245058}, {"id": 260902, "content": "男友说什么女友都同意，把女性的不会拒绝当做贤淑懂事", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 261158, "content": "哭的孩子有糖吃，不哭懂事的孩子没糖吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245072}, {"id": 260903, "content": "“被教授侵犯已经成事实，拆穿两败俱伤，不揭发还能拿高分和推荐信”", "image": null, "praise_count": 425, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 261160, "content": "不吵不闹为人低调", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245089}, {"id": 261161, "content": "多让着你妹妹(弟弟)点\n你都这么大了\n怎么还不懂事！\n      ——即使是我妹妹(弟弟)抢了我的东西\n            不懂事的使坏\n   我不明白，难道年纪小，就可以为所欲为？可以不分黑白？可以随便使坏？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245093}, {"id": 261163, "content": "算了，他还是个孩子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245107}, {"id": 261164, "content": "想要按自己的意愿做事=不成熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868485}, {"id": 261165, "content": "真心=傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242477}, {"id": 261167, "content": "我一直把你当朋友的\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245120}, {"id": 261169, "content": "下面和上面说的都对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468052}, {"id": 261681, "content": "走父母选择的路，过自己不想要的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081385}, {"id": 261170, "content": "憋着闷在心里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245122}, {"id": 261171, "content": "反正没人懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 261939, "content": "必须生孩子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246842}, {"id": 261172, "content": "一个巴掌拍不响 什么狗屁道理 我一个巴掌拍你脸上 你看响不响？嗯？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243419}, {"id": 261174, "content": "这都不会，你还大学生呢。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022023}, {"id": 261175, "content": "这都不会，你还大学生呢。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022023}, {"id": 261176, "content": "这都不会，你还大学生呢。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022023}]}